{"tid":1190061,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【每逢佳節】出道26年！馬浚偉感謝珍姐：沒有她不會有今天的我","createTime":"2019-06-07T06:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T18:55:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba11fe21f730d26447cf6ad4bbb75f197955d80","tid":1190061,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"每逢佳節倍思親，有時不用送貴重禮物、不用經常見面，物輕情義重，感受送禮者用心準備的禮物已經倍感窩心。今年端午節，馬浚偉收到恩師送的素糭，令他有感而發，回想踏入演藝圈的第26個年頭，這份恩情，馬浚偉卻銘記在心。<br />\n馬浚偉今早在微博貼出與大台高層曾勵珍的合照，提起1996年推出第3張個人專輯後，他本來打算離開演藝圈，重回田氏化工有限公司當業務員，繼續跟前老闆田熾先（Jackson Tin）打工。當時珍姐叫他到TVB試鏡，劇本正是《鹿鼎記》，於翌年開拍，馬浚偉亦曾多次公開感謝珍姐的賞識。<br />\n他覺得珍姐教懂他的事情多不勝數，雖然對方是嚴師，對每件事要求超高，亦不接受任何藉口。只要藝人有不對，就是不對，錯就是錯。他回想自己曾被珍姐大罵次數也果真不少，不過他知道珍姐是口硬心軟，只要藝人真心付出、凡事盡心盡力去做，珍姐都願意給對方機會，最後馬浚偉寫道：「我說過，沒有她，馬浚偉早就不在演藝圈了！沒有她，絕對不會有今天的我！今天，藉着這個端午佳節，容我公開謝謝我的恩師！感激我的恩師多年來對我的栽培和關愛，未來，我會更努力，不會辜負你對我的教導！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190607/large/1559884005_b31e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F1559884005_b31e.jpg&h=b0134f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190607/large/1559884039_4d09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F1559884039_4d09.jpg&h=88f9abeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190607/59687251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F59687251&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8urP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=d6a48d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F59687251&h=6b3d2b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190607/59687251</a>"},{"pid":"c7b50ca2958b142d7f84d1d9c090cd4a3641fbdd","tid":1190061,"uid":112316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:29:48.000Z","msg":"契妹"},{"pid":"b42e4571cf036cdfd3d76709209e0ff18ed4ae88","tid":1190061,"uid":96,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"端午節都有得擦鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0238d1fd526cb2e7429a01ee59554e887245e016","tid":1190061,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42e4571cf036cdfd3d76709209e0ff18ed4ae88","tid":1190061,"uid":96,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"端午節都有得擦鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"一個人要擦鞋係冇時候既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59919a76f25b71963a13e1d42c0a04df884a0e8e","tid":1190061,"uid":122703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"每逢佳節倍思珍"},{"pid":"d3884eab1d234304834c2237b663b545fb684034","tid":1190061,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"唔多謝埋樂小姐?"},{"pid":"e91c931b7c6dc90e6ebe07a3b14efc4f89ea9aef","tid":1190061,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"呢個珍姐啲眼光都幾差"},{"pid":"280f46ba42b099bcaed12a0d12bb9aef3f8c0456","tid":1190061,"uid":153305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"有冇做過愛？"},{"pid":"6b6b40ae3811e35704738539e1c0c051ca4c9700","tid":1190061,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"